      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节促销页面</title>\n<style>\n    :root {\n        --red: #D32F2F;\n        --gold: #FFD700;\n        --white: #FFFFFF;\n        --cream: #FDEBD0;\n        --dark: #333333;\n    }\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        color: var(--dark);\n        background-color: var(--cream);\n    }\n    header, nav, section, aside, footer, div {\n        box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    .hero-section {\n        background-color: var(--red);\n        color: var(--white);\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 4rem 2rem;\n    }\n    .hero-section h1 {\n        font-size: 2.5rem;\n        margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n    .hero-section p {\n        font-size: 1.2rem;\n        max-width: 600px;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n    .content-wrapper {\n        max-width: 1200px;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        padding: 2rem;\n    }\n    .price-box {\n        background-color: var(--white);\n        padding: 2rem;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    .price-box h2 {\n        color: var(--red);\n        font-size: 2rem;\n        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n    }\n    .product-info {\n        background-color: var(--white);\n        padding: 2rem;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    .promo-banner {\n        background-color: var(--gold);\n        color: var(--dark);\n        padding: 1.5rem;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    .purchase-flow {\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        gap: 1rem;\n        margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    .purchase-flow label {\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    .purchase-flow button {\n        background-color: var(--red);\n        color: var(--white);\n        border: none;\n        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n    .purchase-flow button:hover {\n        background-color: #b71c1c;\n    }\n    .cart-panel {\n        background-color: var(--white);\n        padding: 1.5rem;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    .category-nav {\n        background-color: var(--white);\n        padding: 1rem;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    .category-nav ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 1rem;\n    }\n    .category-nav li {\n        background-color: var(--cream);\n        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    .coupon-section {\n        background-color: var(--white);\n        padding: 1.5rem;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n        .purchase-flow {\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: flex-start;\n        }\n        .category-nav ul {\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <section class=\"hero-section\" id=\"hero-section\">\n        <h1>春节钜惠，欢乐开启新年</h1>\n        <p>为您甄选优质商品，与家人一同分享春节的喜悦与美好</p>\n    </section>\n    <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n        <section class=\"price-box\" id=\"price-box\">\n            <h2>限时优惠：¥199</h2>\n            <p>原价 ¥299 · 春节专享优惠</p>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"product-info\" id=\"product-info\">\n            <h3>新春礼盒组合</h3>\n            <p>包含精选糖果、坚果及茶叶，适合家庭聚会与亲友赠礼，传递温暖与心意</p>\n        </section>\n        <div class=\"promo-banner\" id=\"promo-banner\">\n            <h4>限时促销 · 抓紧时间</h4>\n            <p>剩余 3 天 · 库存紧张，先到先得</p>\n        </div>\n        <section class=\"purchase-flow\" id=\"purchase-flow\">\n            <label for=\"quantity\">选择数量：</label>\n            <button type=\"button\">加入购物车</button>\n        </section>\n        <aside class=\"cart-panel\" id=\"cart-panel\">\n            <h5>我的购物车</h5>\n            <p>当前暂无商品，请添加您心仪的商品</p>\n        </aside>\n        <nav class=\"category-nav\" id=\"category-nav\">\n            <ul>\n                <li>礼盒</li>\n                <li>零食</li>\n                <li>茶叶</li>\n                <li>饮品</li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n        <section class=\"coupon-section\" id=\"coupon-section\">\n            <h4>领取优惠券</h4>\n            <p>新用户注册即可领取满200减50优惠券，限春节期间使用</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
